    Read GMT file

    read_gmt.Rd

    Imports specified GMT file as a list

    read_gmt(gmt_file_name)

    Arguments

    gmt_file_name

    Character.

    Value

    List of modules, each associated with a character vector containing genes constituting the module.

    Examples

    read_gmt(system.file("extdata", "h.all.v7.4.symbols.gmt", package = "MAYA"))
